Entries.default: "The prince favors you. He has always been a man of deeds, not words."
"We have lost so much of our past. Now, our greatest works of art."
"These tapestries are older than these walls. They have passed through many hands."
"That is a fine bird. Have you come for Hylea's blessing?"
"Poor Ereti. How could this happen to a servant of the queen?"
